Text: Anyone tried this yet? Did it work and is it clean?

The good news is that it's virus-free, but the bad news is that it only *appears* to work, but later you'll find that activation has not been successful.  It's the same old Embrace keygen that worked fine on v8.1.1.4, but not v8.2.8.0.  If you think it worked, just try setting your computer's date up by a month and you'll get the "Non-Licensed Usage" screen (at least that was my experience).  Cheers.
